Beautiful foyer and gorgeous library.  Gourmet kitchen. Elevator goes to third floor attic.  Outside we have 75 acres partial fenced and cross fenced, 28 stall barn, lighted indoor arena and outdoor arena.  Two more out buildings and chicken coop. Sit on the massive 900 sq ft  covered back porch and watch the amazing sunsets
